  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243243.htm", 
  "description": "<p><strong>微软研究院已经为Windows Store带来了一款叫做\"Network Speed Test\"的新应用，能够提供有关上下行速率的详细信息。</strong>该应用可以通过遍布全球的服务器，测量网络延时、下载和上传速率；根据用户的连接速率，为使用者提供能否流畅进行流媒体音乐或视频呼叫等活动的参考信息。滑动到右侧的时候，还可以轻松地查阅比对以往的测速记录。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e1e7af0/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243243.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E9%99%A2%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83Windows+8%E7%89%88%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%B5%8B%E9%80%9F%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243243.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E9%99%A2%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83Windows+8%E7%89%88%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%B5%8B%E9%80%9F%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243243.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E9%99%A2%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83Windows+8%E7%89%88%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%B5%8B%E9%80%9F%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243243.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E9%99%A2%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83Windows+8%E7%89%88%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%B5%8B%E9%80%9F%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243243.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E9%99%A2%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%8