  "date": "Tue, 02 Jul 2013 23:45:54 GMT", 
  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243246.htm", 
  "description": "<p><strong>据美国科技博客TechCrunch的报道，知名技术研究和咨询公司Gartner日前发布的数据报告显示，2013年的全球IT支出预计将达到 3.7万亿美元，较去年仅上涨2%，</strong>其主要原因是价格昂贵的PC和软件等产品逐渐被低价的平板电脑和云服务所代替，同时Gartner还预测2014年全 球的IT支出有望达到3.9万亿美元的规模，同比增长4.1%。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e1e7aee/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243246.htm&amp;t=Gartner%EF%BC%9A2013%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83IT%E6%94%AF%E5%87%BA%E5%B0%86%E8%BE%BE3.7%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243246.htm&amp;t=Gartner%EF%BC%9A2013%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83IT%E6%94%AF%E5%87%BA%E5%B0%86%E8%BE%BE3.7%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243246.htm&amp;t=Gartner%EF%BC%9A2013%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83IT%E6%94%AF%E5%87%BA%E5%B0%86%E8%BE%BE3.7%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243246.htm&amp;t=Gartner%EF%BC%9A2013%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83IT%E6%94%AF%E5%87%BA%E5%B0%86%E8%BE%BE3.7%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243246.htm&amp;t=Gartner%EF%BC%9A2013%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83IT%E6%94%AF%E5%87%BA%E5%B0%86%E8%BE%BE3.7%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BF%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83\" target=\"_blank\"><img 