  "date": "Tue, 02 Jul 2013 23:43:48 GMT", 
  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243244.htm", 
  "description": "<p>“如果3D打印真有用，我的‘郭’字倒过来写。”&#160;富士康董事长郭台铭的公开放言，正映衬着全球热炒的3D打印在目前国内商业化应用领域，不及想象中美好的“尴尬”。<strong>7月2日，在逼仄的车间里，武汉滨湖机电技术产业有限公司（下称“滨湖机电”）总经理周建国无奈表示：“目前，大部分同行生存都很艰难。”作为国内第一批涉足3D打印业务的公司之一，滨湖机电至今亏损年份多过盈利年份。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e1e7aec/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243244.htm&amp;t=%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%97%A0%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%9A3D%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E6%8C%A3%E6%89%8E%E7%9B%88%E4%BA%8F%E7%BA%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243244.htm&amp;t=%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%97%A0%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%9A3D%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E6%8C%A3%E6%89%8E%E7%9B%88%E4%BA%8F%E7%BA%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243244.htm&amp;t=%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%97%A0%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%9A3D%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E6%8C%A3%E6%89%8E%E7%9B%88%E4%BA%8F%E7%BA%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243244.htm&amp;t=%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%97%A0%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%EF%BC%9A3D%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E6%8C%A3%E6%89%8E%E7%9B%88%E4%BA%8F%E7%BA%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243244.htm&amp;t=%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6