  "date": "Tue, 02 Jul 2013 23:42:40 GMT", 
  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243242.htm", 
  "description": "<p>从四年前开始，微软就在不断的强调未来仍然会是Windows的，因为他们将在实现云计算的同时把Windows的产品线延伸至电视、电脑已经手机三个屏幕。目前Windows 8、Windows Phone智能手机平台以及Xbox One平台正在通过不断的融合朝着这一目标前进。<strong>但是让人奇怪的是，微软在此次的开发者大会上却将Xbox One锁在了展示台中，也没有在任何环节向开发者介绍关于Xbox One的应用开发。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e1e7aea/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243242.htm&amp;t=%E9%81%BF%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%B0%88+%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AFXbox+One%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E4%BB%8D%E6%98%AF%E8%B0%9C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243242.htm&amp;t=%E9%81%BF%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%B0%88+%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AFXbox+One%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E4%BB%8D%E6%98%AF%E8%B0%9C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243242.htm&amp;t=%E9%81%BF%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%B0%88+%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AFXbox+One%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E4%BB%8D%E6%98%AF%E8%B0%9C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243242.htm&amp;t=%E9%81%BF%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%B0%88+%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AFXbox+One%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E4%BB%8D%E6%98%AF%E8%B0%9C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243242.htm