  "date": "Tue, 02 Jul 2013 23:41:52 GMT", 
  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243240.htm", 
  "description": "<p>电价一直不菲的日本在福岛核电站事故之后，电力资源变得更加稀缺和昂贵。特别是在夏季用电高峰期，更是采取了1.5倍的峰值电价收费标准。<strong>于是日本人就研发了各种节约能源的家电设备以及控制电费上涨的方法。今天要给各位推荐一个最有创意的方法，就是富士通最新推出的Nokuria X系列空调。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e1e7ae8/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243240.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%AB%E9%80%9A%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E7%94%B5%E8%B4%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83+%E9%81%A5%E6%8E%A7%E5%99%A8%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%9E%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243240.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%AB%E9%80%9A%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E7%94%B5%E8%B4%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83+%E9%81%A5%E6%8E%A7%E5%99%A8%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%9E%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243240.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%AB%E9%80%9A%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E7%94%B5%E8%B4%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83+%E9%81%A5%E6%8E%A7%E5%99%A8%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%9E%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243240.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%AB%E9%80%9A%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E7%94%B5%E8%B4%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83+%E9%81%A5%E6%8E%A7%E5%99%A8%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%9E%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.fe