  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/243231.htm", 
  "description": "<p>现在耗电量最大的智能手机，几乎全部采用锂电池。不少使用者可能一天中要分别充电好几次，但国外知名科技网站近日刊文指出，<strong>每次将电池电量充足，都会造成电池少许退化；更关键的是，要想延长电池寿命，最好别让电池电量耗尽，甚至不要让电量低于20%。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e1e8562/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243231.htm&amp;t=%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E7%A7%98%E8%AF%80%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%95%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E6%80%95%E6%B2%A1%E7%94%B5+%E5%85%85%E6%BB%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243231.htm&amp;t=%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E7%A7%98%E8%AF%80%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%95%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E6%80%95%E6%B2%A1%E7%94%B5+%E5%85%85%E6%BB%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243231.htm&amp;t=%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E7%A7%98%E8%AF%80%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%95%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E6%80%95%E6%B2%A1%E7%94%B5+%E5%85%85%E6%BB%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243231.htm&amp;t=%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E7%A7%98%E8%AF%80%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%95%E5%85%85%E7%94%B5%E6%80%95%E6%B2%A1%E7%94%B5+%E5%85%85%E6%BB%A1%E4%B8%8D%E5%A5%BD\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243231.htm&amp;t=%E6